\c 15
\s Umuntu ongahlala endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*
\d Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 N\nd kosi\nd*, ngubani ozahlala ethenteni lakho\x + Hlab. 24.3,4. Isa. 33.16.\x*? Ngubani ozakwakha entabeni yakho engcwele\x + Hlab. 2.6.\x*?
\v 2 Ngulowo ohamba ngobuqotho\x + Isa. 33.15.\x*, lowenza okulungileyo\x + Hlab. 106.3.\x*, lokhuluma iqiniso enhliziyweni yakhe\x + Zek. 8.16. Efe. 4.25. Joha. 1.47. Kol. 3.9.\x*,
\v 3 ongahlebiyo\x + Levi 19.16. Hlab. 34.13.\x* ngolimi lwakhe\x + 2 Sam. 19.27.\x*, ongenzi okubi kumngane wakhe, longaphakamiseli umakhelwane wakhe ihlazo;
\v 4 olahliweyo uyenyanyeka emehlweni akhe, kodwa uyabahlonipha abayesabayo iN\nd kosi\nd*; ofunga ngoku\add zi\add*limaza, kodwa kaphenduki,
\v 5 onganiki imali yakhe ukuthi azuze inzuzo\x + Eks. 22.25.\x*, longemukeli umvuzo wokuthengwa ngongelacala\x + Eks. 23.8.\x*. Owenza lezizinto kayikunyikinywa kuze kube nininini\x + Hlab. 10.6.\x*.
